{"tid":1299674,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"追究黑警濫權應為首要目標","createTime":"2019-07-09T06:21:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T06:28:40.000Z","uid":35662,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ff34396197a48070e91536ed44814d4118e09a5f","tid":1299674,"uid":35662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:21:51.000Z","msg":"雖然死唔肯用撤回兩個字，但現階段唔應該以撤回修例作出師之名或者作文宣重點。<br />\n<br />\n追究黑警濫權同不追究示威者應為首要目標，否則班狗只會愈黎愈癲，加重我哋行出黎嘅成本。"},{"pid":"5a78ecddd72bec9a15b561c8a2887cb8cac9b801","tid":1299674,"uid":35662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:23:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f2b1f801a074d37ea6050f45ffb150bc15d834c7","tid":1299674,"uid":192587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:24:03.000Z","msg":"推 講真好多人616出黎係因為612警方濫暴但唔洗負責"},{"pid":"1a1cba6d32ebfd06c54a022e3238709c39d99806","tid":1299674,"uid":242260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:27:29.000Z","msg":"支持<br />\n同埋大部分市民，不論政治立場，都係咁諗"},{"pid":"a6574ccbc22180a1cc450c09b46c6920a094aee7","tid":1299674,"uid":35662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:28:06.000Z","msg":"過份執著撤回兩字可能會引起反效果，唔係話放棄，但長期抗爭一定要先減輕自己成本。"},{"pid":"c4da2ca4539de5f2ab3db8ab5b1678d4e58fb52a","tid":1299674,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:28:40.000Z","msg":"連登被帶風向警告, 要求所有連登仔做好文宣和輿論戰準備<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1299371\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1299371</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}